{"title":"矿工的妻子","authors":["唐恒"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工的妻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个矿工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是火的拓取者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我歌唱火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同时也歌唱我的妻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，妻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和煤炭一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是融合在我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色瞳仁里的一个独立的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的身姿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每每我用爱去感应和联想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你总会在属于我开拓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的故事里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，在那深深的地层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在父辈支撑起来的巷道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又开始了黑色与白色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为生活在阳光底下的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为升华不该淡薄的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为烘烤不该冰结的残雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我默默地拧动放炮器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的开关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又操起了“突突”的风钻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力的旋律在胳膊下震颤着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我燃烧的信念便汇入了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子娇嗔的祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像电溜子上下飞泻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的煤流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心也长出了黑色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，妻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你很美丽，也很温柔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和无数矿工的妻子一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有自己的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有自己的轨道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当我告别太阳，走向矿井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你总会伫立在阳台上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者再拉开一道玫瑰色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的窗帘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留给你的只是一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐远去的背影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和那座高高矗立着的煤山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：江西安源煤矿矸石砖厂）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}